node.content:
["Victoria has recorded 1,179\u00a0new COVID-19 infections and six\u00a0deaths, taking the death toll in the current Delta outbreak to 518.", "The new cases were detected from 74,252\u00a0test results processed on Tuesday, and take the state's number of active infections to 11,959.", "There are 299\u00a0COVID-19 patients in Victorian hospitals, 43\u00a0active cases in intensive care, with 18\u00a0patients on ventilators.", "More to come.", "", "
